  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You whip air currents around your hands and generate a dust cloud cloaking yourself and anyone in the radius of this jutsu in a thick cloud of dust and debris. All creatures are treated as if they have total cover while inside the cloud, from creatures outside the cloud and vice versa. This total cover does not prevent attacks or jutsu from entering or exiting the cloud. Creatures other than you have disadvantage on perception checks to see through the cloud if they have special vision like Chakra Sight. Also, creatures other than you, vision, is treated as if they are in dim light while inside the cloud.</p>",
